        public static CoolStuffIncPriceData parseCSIHTML(String htmlContent,
                                 long csiID)
                                          throws Throwable
        This is a static method used to parse out CoolStuffIncPriceData content from the provided HTML page. This method should generate a complete object or fail.
        Parameters:
        htmlContent - The HTML page we asked for.
        csiID - Need to provide this value since it's not actually in the page to be parsed.
        Returns:
        a CoolStuffIncPriceData object fully formed.
        Throws:
        Throwable - Throws this error if there were any parsing issues encountered.
